<h4>Passing ID parameter in URL</h4>
<h4>Using normal anchor href - </h4>
<a href="/Home/Edit/1">Get id by click on link</a>
<br />
<h4>Using MVC5 html helper method with ActionLink - </h4>
@Html.ActionLink("Get id by click on link","Edit","Home", new {id = 1});
<br />
<h4>Using MVC5 html helper method with Anchor - </h4>
<a href="@Url.Action("Edit","Home", new {id = 1})">Get id by click on link</a>
<br />
<h3>Using TAG helper - with asp-controller and asp-action </h3>
<a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="1">Get id by click on link</a>
<br />